Comment: 0,0:01:05.96,0:01:06.00,OPJP,,0,0,0,,OPJP Start
Comment: 0,0:01:17.89,0:01:20.81,OPJP,,0,0,0,karaoke,大切な落とし物を
Comment: 0,0:01:20.81,0:01:23.48,OPJP,,0,0,0,karaoke,知らない君が拾って
Comment: 0,0:01:23.48,0:01:26.27,OPJP,,0,0,0,karaoke,届けてくれたみたいな
Comment: 0,0:01:26.27,0:01:29.28,OPJP,,0,0,0,karaoke,思いがけない朝
Comment: 0,0:01:29.28,0:01:32.16,OPJP,,0,0,0,karaoke,そういえば大事なものは
Comment: 0,0:01:32.16,0:01:34.91,OPJP,,0,0,0,karaoke,ちゃんと名前を書かなくじゃ
Comment: 0,0:01:34.91,0:01:37.91,OPJP,,0,0,0,karaoke,どこかで失くしてしまうと
Comment: 0,0:01:37.91,0:01:40.79,OPJP,,0,0,0,karaoke,よく言われてたのに
Comment: 0,0:01:40.79,0:01:43.58,OPJP,,0,0,0,karaoke,誰かの　せいじゃなくて
Comment: 0,0:01:43.58,0:01:46.34,OPJP,,0,0,0,karaoke,誰かの　ものでもなくて
Comment: 0,0:01:46.34,0:01:49.13,OPJP,,0,0,0,karaoke,変わらず　世界は
Comment: 0,0:01:49.13,0:01:51.59,OPJP,,0,0,0,karaoke,そこにあるよ
Comment: 0,0:01:51.59,0:01:54.43,OPJP,,0,0,0,karaoke,風と　さあ手と手繋いで
Comment: 0,0:01:54.43,0:01:57.26,OPJP,,0,0,0,karaoke,空と　息を合わせて
Comment: 0,0:01:57.26,0:01:59.77,OPJP,,0,0,0,karaoke,行こう　動き出した
Comment: 0,0:01:59.77,0:02:03.14,OPJP,,0,0,0,karaoke,心の矢印
Comment: 0,0:02:03.14,0:02:05.86,OPJP,,0,0,0,karaoke,君と　そう君とならば
Comment: 0,0:02:05.86,0:02:09.32,OPJP,,0,0,0,karaoke,ならば　そう君とだから
Comment: 0,0:02:09.32,0:02:17.33,OPJP,,0,0,0,karaoke,何が起きるかなんかわからない未来が
Comment: 0,0:02:17.33,0:02:19.20,OPJP,,0,0,0,karaoke,走る
Comment: 0,0:02:19.20,0:02:23.83,OPJP,last,0,0,0,karaoke,キラキラ　跳ねてる
Comment: 0,0:02:35.97,0:02:36.01,OPJP,,0,0,0,,OPJP End
Comment: 0,0:01:05.96,0:01:06.00,OPCN,,0,0,0,,OPCN Start
Comment: 0,0:01:17.89,0:01:20.81,OPCN,,0,0,0,karaoke,我那珍貴的失物
Comment: 0,0:01:20.81,0:01:23.48,OPCN,,0,0,0,karaoke,被素不相識的你撿起
Comment: 0,0:01:23.48,0:01:26.27,OPCN,,0,0,0,karaoke,把它交還給我
Comment: 0,0:01:26.27,0:01:29.28,OPCN,,0,0,0,karaoke,出乎意料的清晨
Comment: 0,0:01:29.28,0:01:32.16,OPCN,,0,0,0,karaoke,這麼說來　重要的東西
Comment: 0,0:01:32.16,0:01:34.91,OPCN,,0,0,0,karaoke,一定要寫上名字
Comment: 0,0:01:34.91,0:01:37.91,OPCN,,0,0,0,karaoke,不然會丟失於不知何處
Comment: 0,0:01:37.91,0:01:40.79,OPCN,,0,0,0,karaoke,經常被這樣告誡
Comment: 0,0:01:40.79,0:01:43.58,OPCN,,0,0,0,karaoke,不是任何人的錯
Comment: 0,0:01:43.58,0:01:46.34,OPCN,,0,0,0,karaoke,也不屬於任何人
Comment: 0,0:01:46.34,0:01:49.13,OPCN,,0,0,0,karaoke,一成不變的世界
Comment: 0,0:01:49.13,0:01:51.59,OPCN,,0,0,0,karaoke,存在於此
Comment: 0,0:01:51.59,0:01:54.43,OPCN,,0,0,0,karaoke,隨風　來吧手牽手
Comment: 0,0:01:54.43,0:01:57.26,OPCN,,0,0,0,karaoke,於空　配合對方步調
Comment: 0,0:01:57.26,0:01:59.77,OPCN,,0,0,0,karaoke,走吧　出發了
Comment: 0,0:01:59.77,0:02:03.14,OPCN,,0,0,0,karaoke,心之所向
Comment: 0,0:02:03.14,0:02:05.86,OPCN,,0,0,0,karaoke,與你　沒錯　如果與你一起
Comment: 0,0:02:05.86,0:02:09.32,OPCN,,0,0,0,karaoke,沒錯　正因為與你一起
Comment: 0,0:02:09.32,0:02:17.33,OPCN,,0,0,0,karaoke,向著未知的未來
Comment: 0,0:02:17.33,0:02:19.20,OPCN,,0,0,0,karaoke,奔跑
Comment: 0,0:02:19.20,0:02:23.83,OPCN,last,0,0,0,karaoke,閃耀奪目
Comment: 0,0:02:35.47,0:02:35.51,OPCN,,0,0,0,,OPCN End
